## Timeline: What Happens During a Measurement Session

```
[User clicks button12 - DDA]
  ?
BeginPerformanceMeasurement("DDA")
  ??? Checks IsSlow("DDA") from slowModes dictionary
  ??? Calls PerformanceMonitor.BeginMeasurement("DDA", isSlowMode=false)
      ??? Records startTime = Stopwatch.GetTimestamp()
      ??? Records startMemory = GC.GetTotalMemory(false)
      ??? Returns PerformanceMeasurementToken with these values
  ?
ClearCanvas()
RunDDA(50, 50, 100, 300, Color.Red, bmp, pictureBox1)
  ??? Algorithm executes normally (completely unaware of monitoring)
  ?
EndPerformanceMeasurement()
  ??? Calls PerformanceMonitor.EndMeasurement(_currentPerfToken)
      ??? Records endTime = Stopwatch.GetTimestamp()
      ??? Calculates elapsed = (endTime - startTime) * 1000 / Stopwatch.Frequency
      ??? Queries CPU usage from PerformanceCounter
      ??? Records endMemory = GC.GetTotalMemory(false)
      ??? Calculates memoryDelta = endMemory - startMemory
      ??? Creates PerformanceSnapshot with all metrics
      ??? Stores snapshot in _metricsHistory["DDA"]
      ??? Returns snapshot
  ?
UpdatePerformanceDisplay("DDA", snapshot)
  ??? Formats display text
  ??? Gets comparison data from PerformanceMonitor.GetPerformanceComparison()
  ??? Updates lblPerformanceMetrics.Text (thread-safe via Invoke)
  ?
[User sees metrics label update on the right side of the window]
```

