## How to Add Performance Monitoring to a New Algorithm

### Step 1: Identify the algorithm key (must match slowModes dictionary)
```csharp
string algorithmName = "MyNewAlgorithm";
```

### Step 2: Wrap the execution
```csharp
private void MyButton_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)
{
    BeginPerformanceMeasurement("MyNewAlgorithm");    // ADD THIS
    
    ClearCanvas();
    // ... your drawing code ...
    MyDrawingAlgorithm();
    
    pictureBox1.Image = bmp;
    EndPerformanceMeasurement();                       // ADD THIS
}
```

### Step 3: Done!
The system automatically:
- Detects slow/fast mode from `IsSlow("MyNewAlgorithm")`
- Measures execution time, CPU, memory
- Stores snapshots in history
- Updates the display label

**No other changes needed!**

